            <div class="section-title text-center">
                <div class="title-text">
                    <h2>What is STP?(Systematic Transfer Plan)</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="mb-5">Systematic Transfer Plan or STP is an investment plan that allows investors to invest a
                    lump sum amount in a particular mutual fund and regularly transfer a specific amount into another
                    fund.
                    For instance, the investor can choose to transfer a pre-defined amount from a debt fund to an equity
                    fund (or vice versa) on a regular basis.
                    For this to happen, the units from one fund are sold and the money is used to purchase units in the
                    equity fund.

                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="row">

                <div class="mx-auto col-xl-10 col-lg-10 col-md-12 col-sm-10 col-12">
